text: Liliane Becker (9 November 1942 - 14 September 1981) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Luxembourgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
